{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日早上仍然較涼，天色較為明朗。星期四氣溫回升，接近週末天氣漸轉不穩定。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月5日(二)</cell>\n        <cell>5月6日(三)</cell>\n        <cell>5月7日(四)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>20度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東風4至5級，初時離岸及高地間中6級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4級，離岸間中5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風3至4級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>80-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中高</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>多雲，間中有驟雨。初時局部地區有雷暴。天氣稍涼。稍後驟雨逐漸減少。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。初時有一兩陣微雨，日間部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有一兩陣驟雨。日間短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月8日(五)</cell>\n        <cell>5月9日(六)</cell>\n        <cell>5月10日(日)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>30度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>微風2級，稍後東北風3級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風4至5級，離岸及高地間中6級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4級，初時5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>65-95%</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n        <cell>60-85%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>短暫時間有陽光，有幾陣驟雨。稍後局部地區有狂風雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。初時有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n        <cell>短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-04T23:16:07.805573+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":502,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}